org.apache.poi.poifs.property

Class PropertyTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.poifs.property.PropertyTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BATManaged 

    public final class PropertyTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements BATManaged
    This class embodies the Property Table for a POIFSFileSystem; this is basically the directory for all of the documents in the filesystem and looks up entries in the filesystem to their chain of blocks.(这个类体现了POIFSFileSystem的属性表;这基本上是文件系统中所有文档的目录，并在文件系统中查找其块链的条目。)

        java.io.IOException - if anything goes wrong (which should be a result of the input being NFG)(java.io. IOResponse-如果出现任何问题（这应该是输入为NFG的结果）)
